com.example.habitup.Model

Class HabitList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.habitup.Model.HabitList

  • public class HabitList
extends java.lang.Object
    HabitList represents the current user's list of habits. It can be used to add or delete a habit from the user's habit list. It stores the habits in a linked hash map where the habit's name is the key and the habit object is the value.

    • Constructor Summary

      HabitList()
